trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture"> </xref> händelse.

trans-unit.source: The results from the gesture recognizer.
trans-unit.target: Resultaten från gesttolk.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a Boolean value that indicates whether strokes should be considered a gesture.
trans-unit.target: Hämtar eller anger ett booleskt värde som anger om linjer ska betraktas som en gest.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture> event occurs, the value of the Cancel property depends on the first <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult> in the collection returned by the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.GetGestureRecognitionResults%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: När den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture>händelse inträffar, värdet på egenskapen Avbryt beror på först <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult>i samlingen som returneras av den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.GetGestureRecognitionResults%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.GetGestureRecognitionResults%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas.Gesture>

trans-unit.source: If the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.ApplicationGesture%2A> property is <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>, or if it is a gesture whose <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A> is a value other than <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>, then Cancel is `true`.
trans-unit.target: Om värdet för den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.ApplicationGesture%2A>egenskapen är <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>, eller om det är en gest vars <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A>är ett värde annat än <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>, då är Avbryt `true`.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.ApplicationGesture%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, Cancel is `false`.
trans-unit.target: Annars Avbryt är `false`.

trans-unit.source: When Cancel is `false`, the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas> adds the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.Strokes%2A> to its <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection>.
trans-unit.target: När Avbryt är `false`, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>lägger <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.Strokes%2A>till dess <xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection>.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.StrokeCollection> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.Strokes%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>

trans-unit.source: When Cancel is `true`, the strokes are not added to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>.
trans-unit.target: När Avbryt är `true`, strokes har inte lagts till i <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvas>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the strokes are ink; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if the strokes are a gesture.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om linjerna pennanteckningar; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> om linjerna är en gest.

trans-unit.source: Returns results from the gesture recognizer.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar resultatet från gesttolk.

trans-unit.source: The collection returned by the GetGestureRecognitionResults method is sorted by the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Den samling som returneras av metoden GetGestureRecognitionResults sorteras efter den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult.RecognitionConfidence%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For example, GetGestureRecognitionResults might return a collection of <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult> objects with the following values: |Index|ApplicationGesture|RecognitionConfidence| |-----------|------------------------|---------------------------| |0|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |1|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |2|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |3|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>|<xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| This means that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> recognizes that it is very likely that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> is a check mark, relatively likely that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> in not a gesture, and not at all likely that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> is a curlicue or a double curlicue.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel GetGestureRecognitionResults kan returnera en samling <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult>objekt med följande värden: | Indexet | ApplicationGesture | RecognitionConfidence | |-----------|------------------------|---------------------------| |&0; | <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>| <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |&1; | <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>| <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |&2; | <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>| <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| |&3; | <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>| <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>| Detta innebär att den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer>identifierar att det är mycket troligt som den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke>är markerat, relativt sannolikt som den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke>i inte en gest och inte alls sannolikt som den <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke>är en curlicue eller dubbla curlicue.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognizer> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.GestureRecognitionResult>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The GetGestureRecognitionResults method can return an array with <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture> with a higher degree of <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> than it has for other application gestures.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I GetGestureRecognitionResults metoden kan returnera en matris med <xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>med en högre grad av <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>än vad som finns för andra program gester.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.ApplicationGesture>

trans-unit.source: This means that it is more likely that the <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke> is not a gesture, as opposed to a gesture that has a lower <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>.
trans-unit.target: Det innebär att det är troligare som <xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke>är inte en gest, till skillnad från en gest som har en lägre <xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence>.</xref:System.Windows.Ink.RecognitionConfidence> </xref:System.Windows.Ink.Stroke>

trans-unit.target: En samling av möjliga programmet gester som den <xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.Strokes*>kanske.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.InkCanvasGestureEventArgs.Strokes*>
